Maxima glared back at Hevn. Especially when her greetings were to the 
newcomers & he rudely interrupted. Let alone, she was not aware of an intruder. 

She growled at Hevn as her crimson optics glowed .. a warning that he best be 
quiet until his time to speak. For now, this was her playing arena. 

She turned back to the newcomers. Awaiting their response.

--part1_a.30f86e11.2c07d142_boundary
